ENDCLASS.



CLASS ZCL_BIER_OBERGAERIG IMPLEMENTATION.


* <SIGNATURE>---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
* | Instance Public Method ZCL_BIER_OBERGAERIG->BRAUEN
* +-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
* +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</SIGNATURE>
  method BRAUEN.

    CALL METHOD super->brauen."*2
    WRITE: /'Sogar obergärig'."*3

  endmethod.


