* +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</SIGNATURE>
  method SET_ALKOHOLGEHALT.


  endmethod.


* <SIGNATURE>---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
* | Instance Public Method ZCL_BIER_OBERGAERIG->WRITE_STAMMWUERZE
* +-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
* +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</SIGNATURE>
  METHOD write_stammwuerze.
    WRITE: / 'Obergärige Stammwürze: '.
    super->write_stammwuerze( ).
  ENDMETHOD.
